---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Contact" description="Get in touch with the MoodSupplement team.">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-5 pt-12 pb-16">
    <p class="eyebrow mb-3">Contact</p>
    <h1 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-moss-deep">Get in touch</h1>
    <div class="prose-mr mt-6">
      <p>Questions, corrections, or feedback on a supplement profile? We'd like to hear from you. Accuracy matters to us, so if you spot something that needs fixing, please let us know.</p>
      <p>Email: <a href="mailto:hello@moodsupplement.net">hello@moodsupplement.net</a></p>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-soft"><em>Placeholder address — replace with your real contact email, or wire up a form provider (e.g. Formspree, Netlify Forms) before launch.</em></p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
